Interface HTMLAppletElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.w3c.dom.Element, HTMLElement, org.w3c.dom.Node

    public interface HTMLAppletElement
extends HTMLElement
    An embedded Java applet. See the APPLET element definition in HTML 4.01.
